{"tid":597888,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[廢老恩物]斯諾登：Facebook 實際上是偽裝過的「監視公司」","createTime":"2018-03-19T05:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T08:16:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"61f62f4d98399f93b6026cb2738895f4e2b0df06","tid":597888,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"有關美國總統 Trump 的競選手段一再被爆出問題，除了利用 Facebook 散播假新聞，最近更被發現數據公司劍橋分析 ( Cambridge Analytica ) 當時在未經允許的情況下擅自收集 Facebook 用戶資訊，使公司能準確針對用戶為該競選團隊推出政治廣告，影響人數達千萬人。<br />\n<br />\n儘管 Facebook 已與該公司劃清界線，但是前中情局職員愛德華斯諾登 Edward Snowden 最近仍在 Twitter 上抨擊 Facebook 與其他社交媒體，更直言：「Facebook 不是受害者，他們是共犯。」<br />\n<br />\n斯諾登近期發表了推文，表示社交媒體實際上是偽裝過的「監視公司」：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以收集和販賣詳細私生活紀錄的公司過去是以「監視公司」為名義自居。不過他們後來自稱為「社交媒體」，這是美國戰爭部改名為國防部後最為成功的騙局。<br />\nBusinesses that make money by collecting and selling detailed records of private lives were once plainly described as &ldquo;surveillance companies.&rdquo; Their rebranding as &ldquo;social media&rdquo; is the most successful deception since the Department of War became the Department of Defense.</strong><br />\n<br />\n而針對 Facebook 上大量用戶資訊遭劍橋數據不當收集的事件，他也不認為 Facebook 是受害者，反倒是他們的共犯：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/19/edward-snowden-said-social-media-are-surveillance-companies/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2Fedward-snowden-said-social-media-are-surveillance-companies%2F&d=TMpmTYxyytHSiUfDdv5Qn2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=ddd468d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/19/edward-snowden-said-social-media-are-surveillance-companies/</a>"},{"pid":"7ada0749310509243abdb15bdb9461c2fb9b0bc2","tid":597888,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T05:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/142556_b14f0a4a6cd1ebbac3e71dfcf1ab98b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F